{"data":[{"date":"09:54 15/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1: C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/15/diem-nhan-sau-tran-hagl-31-can-tho-cong-dau-cua-van-toan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hay Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng HAGL, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</h2><h2>1. M\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL sau pha b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ebfm th\u1ea5y c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng treo b\u00f3ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a V\u0103n S\u01a1n, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o qu\u00ea H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o g\u00f3c xa, \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i T\u00f4 V\u0129nh L\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ecfng, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong 45 ph\u00fat hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/anh3_2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n To\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt ph\u00fat, V\u0103n To\u00e0n l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edb t\u1edbi sau pha d\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng xu\u1ed1ng bi\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhanh b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1\u00a0tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u1ecdn c\u1ed7 v\u00e0o trong cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Osmar l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 3 trong 4 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, V\u0103n To\u00e0n \u0111\u00f3ng vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng cho HAGL. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh hay tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 2-2 t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Nam, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u1eadp nh\u1eefng c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u r\u1ea5t vui cho HAGL trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong t\u1ed1p 3 khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n ngo\u1ea1i binh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Osmar Francisco ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho HAGL. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n cho \u2018G\u1ed7\u2019 tuy nhi\u00ean h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-4 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Osmar ghi b\u00e0n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u0169ng x\u00f3a tan \u0111i nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i SLNA. L\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u00f3c, Osmar nhanh ch\u00f3ng th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i HAGL.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/aGFnbF9jb25ncGh1b25nX2FubXVuZw==.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 b\u1eaft nh\u1ecbp nhanh c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u m\u1eebng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai khi m\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ngo\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Osmar, c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Zeba Josip, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh m\u1edbi n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a HAGL. \u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, Zeba \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 theo k\u00e8m ch\u00e2n s\u00fat nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, Patiyo. Ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a HAGL th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e3 mang l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. \u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a \u2018G\u1ed7\u2019<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 s\u01a1 h\u1edf \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. N\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Pleiku \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 1 khi b\u00f3ng d\u1ed9i v\u00e0o x\u00e0 ngang b\u1eadt ra sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Ho\u00e0ng Vissai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u00ean h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 HAGL v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00fat 61 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ngo\u1ea1i binh Wander Luiz b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb theo k\u00e8m \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft t\u1eeb pha t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. B\u00f3ng \u0111i hi\u1ec3m khi\u1ebfn V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng khi T\u0103ng Tu\u1ea5n lao v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i \u0111i h\u01a1i cao so v\u1edbi x\u00e0 ngang HAGL. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c khai th\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a HAGL b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec3 Patiyo lao\u00a0v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf trong kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a HAGL. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n th\u00eam k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<h2>4. Th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi b\u1ecb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a t\u1ed1 ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o th\u00eam r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i khi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n x\u00f4 x\u00e1t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Quang T\u00ecnh b\u00ean ph\u00eda C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 10 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 pha tranh b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau v\u1edbi Quang T\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e0n anh b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch, khi\u1ebfn Quang T\u00ecnh b\u1ecb ng\u00e3. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady, c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o ng\u1ef1c C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 779px;\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width: 777px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width: 777px;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width: 769px;\"><img alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 C\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/cp-quangtinh.jpg\" style=\"border: none;\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HAGL vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat CLB HA Gia Lai c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng v\u1eeba khi \u0111\u1ecbnh lao v\u00e0o tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u0169a, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. R\u1ea5t may sau \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp can ng\u0103n hai c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00f3ng. C\u1ea3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Quang T\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u. \u1ede v\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o l\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng hay v\u00e0 d\u00f9ng ch\u00e2n t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ki\u1ec1m ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, b\u1edfi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng n\u1eefa, anh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 1 tr\u1eadn. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng.</p>\r\n<h2>5. C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 t\u1ee5t s\u00e2u tr\u00ean BXH<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c TP.HCM b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u00ecm s\u00e2u trong kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 12 tr\u00ean BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. C\u00f3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady h\u1ecd m\u1edbi tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau vong 19\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018 sau v\u00f2ng 19\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/BXH-V-League.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>BXH V-League 2018 sau v\u00f2ng 19</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4235","checkdouble":"191237"},{"date":"10:04 15/07","title":"Real Madrid h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Mateo Kovacic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/2/real-madrid-het-gia-khong-tuong-cho-mateo-kovacic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid b\u00e1n Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kovacic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Modric v\u00e0 Kroos. Los Blancos v\u1eeba kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Modric \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid b\u00e1n Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid b\u00e1n Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/real-madrid-het-gia-khong-tuong-cho-mateo-kovacic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh quan t\u00e2m Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 Kovacic nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin Kovacic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u1ede Anh, c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, bao g\u1ed3m MU, Man City v\u00e0 Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-sao-real-madrid-172-189650.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU nh\u1eafm Kovacic thay th\u1ebf Carrick</span>, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7. Tottenham mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia thay th\u1ebf cho Dembele, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City \u0111ang th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf so v\u1edbi Chelsea \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Jorginho, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994. Man xanh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau\u00a0m\u1ed9 c\u1ef1u sao Inter Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real \u0111\u00f2i 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid b\u00e1n Mateo Kovacic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Daily Star kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Los Blancos \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real vs PSG Kovacic\" title=\"Real vs PSG Kovacic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/mu-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-sao-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua Kovacic t\u1eeb Inter Milan, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. D\u00f9 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, song h\u1ecd kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Real h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, Kovacic s\u1ebd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0 \u1edf c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng xong. N\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Modric v\u00e0 Kroos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4234","checkdouble":"191234"},{"date":"10:41 15/07","title":"Ch\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/6/chot-thoi-diem-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i hay \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Bale b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Bale b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh r\u1ea5t vui khi CR7 ra \u0111i, b\u1edfi khi \u0111\u00f3 Bale s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Lopetegui h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/chot-thoi-diem-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Gareth Bale\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bale s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh khi m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Donbalon th\u00ec l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng Bale \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Lopetegui c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Isco v\u00e0 Asensio, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng n\u00e0y tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN v\u00e0 gh\u1ebb l\u1ea1nh Bale l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Real \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Eden Hazard c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Gareth Bale lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i hay \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" title=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bale s\u1ebd b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n n\u1ebfu Lopetegui t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Daily Mail, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Bale l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real, n\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t th\u00eam Bale tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1ecb x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/real-giam-gia-ban-gareth-bale-cho-mu-172-184790.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Bale</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tottenham v\u00e0 Bayern Munich c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4233","checkdouble":"191238"},{"date":"09:48 15/07","title":"Mourinho g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u1edbn khi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/mourinho-gap-kho-khan-lon-khi-chuan-bi-truoc-mua-giai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i, nh\u01b0ng HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 World Cup, khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang M\u1ef9, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1 gi\u1ea3i ICC v\u00e0 t\u00edch l\u0169y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 &ldquo;pre-season&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u01a1n 10 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, v\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 (c\u1ee7a Anh, Ph\u00e1p, B\u1ec9) chinh chi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho Premier League ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y&rdquo; &ndash; Jose Mourinho t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, &ldquo;b\u1edfi v\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga. \u0110\u00f3 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y \u0111i c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t\" title=\"Pogba vs Fellaini\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Paul-Pogba-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Phap-va-ban-than-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y \u0111i c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;3 tu\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, tinh th\u1ea7n, \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 quay l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. \u0110\u01b0a h\u1ecd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u01b0? OK th\u00f4i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t h\u1ecd v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong 3-4 th\u00e1ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 3 tu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ngay trong tu\u1ea7n Premier League khai m\u1ea1c, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7&rdquo; &ndash; Mourinho ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 World Cup.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 5/8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Bayern Munich. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t chia s\u1ebb, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1ef1 d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t. \u1ede k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp theo, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00f2n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, khi n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qatar s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup 2022 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester-172-191192.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester-172-191192.html\">Th\u00eam b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y M.U s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 M.U.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh-421-191201.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/roy-keane-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-that-bai-cua-dt-anh-421-191201.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e9p v\u1ebf v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 trong tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng Ba tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i M.U Roy Keane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4232","checkdouble":"191232"},{"date":"10:10 15/07","title":"Kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Hazard, tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Chelsea tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u1edf l\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>K\u1ebft th\u00fac World Cup 2018, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Eden Hazard, Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid, anh tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i qua, Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Ngay sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng r\u1eddi CLB Chelsea sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAi c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft Hazard \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea7m m\u1eaft v\u1ec1 Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi anh trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i. Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 gia nh\u1eadp, t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hazard tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea m\u00f9a n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng l\u00e0 Maurizio Sarri b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Jorginho.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Hazard, Thibaut Courtois c\u0169ng n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, anh cho bi\u1ebft v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois noi ve tuong lai\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/courtois-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 xem \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea\u201d, t\u1edd Marca tr\u00edch l\u1eddi Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u1ecd c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng CLB s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, ngay c\u1ea3 khi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c \u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, b\u1edfi v\u00ec t\u00f4i th\u00edch th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 London.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0 <br>\r\nCourtois \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 n\u0103m 2011 t\u1eeb Genk. Anh tr\u1ea3i qua 3 n\u0103m d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-hazard-dich-than-tuyen-bo-muon-roi-chelsea-172-191203.html\">N\u00f3ng: Hazard \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nongs-hazard-sap-co-ben-do-moi-172-191182.html\">N\u00d3NG: Eden Hazard s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-chinh-thuc-bo-nhiem-nguoi-thay-the-conte-172-191167.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Chelsea CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Conte</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4231","checkdouble":"191236"},{"date":"10:35 15/07","title":"Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Lovren \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-lovren-va-dang-cap-cua-hoc-tro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lovren v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf Liverpool \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean b\u1ed5 sung r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u00fd ki\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch quan.</h2><h2><br>\r\nLovren \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nDejan Lovren v\u00e0 \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh, n\u01a1i trung v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m trung phong xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc Harry Kane c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i im ti\u1ebfng. Sau tr\u1eadn, Lovren \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ecbp \u201cn\u1ed5 to\u201d khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Lovren tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u1ea3 l\u00e0 su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia s\u1ed1ng trong nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m khi\u1ebfn CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n ch\u1ecbu nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lovren v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lovren v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Klopp-phat-bieu-ve-Lovren-voi-nhung-loi-ca-ngoi-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lovren ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKlopp \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nKlopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lovren v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u00d4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng song c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t \u00fd ki\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch quan h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y. \u201cS\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu ai \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Dejan! Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00f3i \u0111\u00fang\u201d, Klopp n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111i v\u00e0o chi ti\u1ebft, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Croatia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Rakitic, Brozovic, Modric v\u00ec v\u1eady c\u1ea7n ai \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t ph\u00eda sau. Dejan l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u00f3.\u201d <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lovren\" title=\"Lovren\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/11/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-lovren-va-dang-cap-cua-hoc-tro.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Lovren v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, Klopp c\u0169ng nh\u1eafc kh\u00e9o Lovren c\u1ea7n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u201cDejan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u00e0 3 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft Europa League. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, song v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m \u1edf s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng nhau trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 HLV Klopp tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-ve-tan-binh-shaqiri-cua-liverpool-172-191149.html\">HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Shaqiri c\u1ee7a Liverpool?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-daniel-sturridge-172-190783.html\">Klopp l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Daniel Sturridge</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/henderson-phat-bieu-ve-klopp-421-190774.html\">Jurgen Klopp \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-mung-ro-voi-man-trinh-dien-cua-2-tan-binh-bom-tan-172-190681.html\">Klopp m\u1eebng r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a 2 t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4230","checkdouble":"191240"},{"date":"11:09 15/07","title":"M\u1edbi t\u1edbi Chelsea, Sarri \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n thanh l\u00fd \u201ct\u00e0n d\u01b0\u201d th\u1eddi Conte","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/20/hlv-sarri-muon-ban-giroud-va-morata.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Giroud v\u00e0 Morata, 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Conte. \u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Napoli mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 tr\u00f2 c\u0169 Higuain t\u1ea1i Chelsea.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ednh t\u1ed1ng kh\u1ee9 Giroud v\u00e0 Morata</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlvaro Morata gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea t\u1eeb Real Madrid m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Morata \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Zinedine Zidane n\u00edu gi\u1eef.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi t\u1edbi Chelsea, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n n\u0103ng \u201cs\u00e1t th\u1ee7\u201d. 48 tr\u1eadn tr\u00f4i qua tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00f9a 2017/18, Morata ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 15 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n n\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Real c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i CLB m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Giroud v\u00e0 Morata, 2 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Giroud v\u00e0 Morata, 2 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/20/hlv-sarri-muon-ban-giroud-va-morata.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Giroud v\u00e0 Morata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 k\u00e9m duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Morata khi\u1ebfn Chelsea ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Olivier Giroud t\u1eeb Arsenal \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u201cch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y\u201d. Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Giroud l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i nh\u01b0ng anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 \u201cb\u1eadt b\u00e3i\u201d kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea3 l\u00e0 HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Giroud v\u00e0 Morata. T\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ea3 Giroud v\u00e0 Morata \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7u trong khi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Sarri l\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mu\u1ed1n mang v\u1ec1 Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00eda sau thanh l\u00fd \u201ct\u00e0n d\u01b0\u201d c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Conte, Sarri mu\u1ed1n m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho tr\u00f2 c\u0169 Gonzalo Higuain t\u1edbi Chelsea. M\u00f9a 2015/16, khi c\u1ea3 hai h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c t\u1ea1i Napoli, Higuain \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 38 b\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 sau 42 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gonzalo Higuain cua Juventus\" title=\"Gonzalo Higuain cua Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/chelsea-sap-co-tien-dao-tri-gia-53-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Higuain t\u1ea1i Juventus c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t lung lay. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo khi\u1ebfn anh \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh. Th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb Italia cho hay ph\u00eda Juve s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Higuain \u0111\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1edbi Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Sarri l\u1ea1i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea. M\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb 55 t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u Euro l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u00fap The Blues c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Higuain.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 HLV Sarri tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/giai-quyet-xong-conte-chelsea-chuan-bi-don-lien-3-tan-binh-172-191166.html\">Gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong Conte, Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n li\u1ec1n 3 t\u00e2n binh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-neu-hlv-sarri-dan-dat-chelsea-thay-conte-172-191110.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4229","checkdouble":"191241"},{"date":"23:11 14/07","title":"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-cua-hagl-truoc-can-tho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League 2018, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. V\u0103n To\u00e0n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Osmar trong hi\u1ec7p 2.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh chia s\u1ebb: \u201c\u1ede nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00f9a m\u01b0a \u1ea9m \u01b0\u1edbt, kh\u00ed h\u1eadu thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t, n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-cua-hagl-truoc-can-tho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n To\u00e0n g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai cho hay: \"Sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p\u00a0Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a BVN, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ed1i nh\u1eb9 n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 em ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i k\u00e9o Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e1 gi\u1eefa c\u00f9ng Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf hi\u1ec7p hai nh\u01b0ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khen ng\u1ee3i. HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh\u00a0n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \"Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Trong th\u1eddi gian qua, em l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i. Ngo\u00e0i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n gi\u00fap kh\u1eafc ch\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng Ninh cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cC\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng qua 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p CLB Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u0169ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n th\u00f4i, n\u00f3i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00e2u gi\u1edd th\u00ec tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3 Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, d\u1ec5 \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn chi\u1ec1u nay, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103ng n\u1ed5, ch\u1ea1y nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i. Nh\u1eefng pha va ch\u1ea1m d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng do l\u1ed7i ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, HAGL s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p SLNA. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tinh th\u1ea7n cho chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Vinh\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u0169ng khen h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung h\u01a1n song \u00f4ng v\u1eabn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng, \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu m\u00e0 \u2018G\u1ed7\u2019 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-can-tho-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191160.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/hagl-vs-can-tho-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-can-tho-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191160.html\">HAGL 3-1 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 (KT): Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u00f3t tim</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 19 V-League.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4228","checkdouble":"191193"},{"date":"22:26 14/07","title":"HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ch\u00ea kh\u00e9o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL sau cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/17/hlv-can-tho-che-kheo-cau-thu-hagl-nam-san-qua-nhieu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u00e2u gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 chi\u1ec1u 14/7.</h2><h2>HLV\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ch\u00ea c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL\u00a0</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ch\u00ea kh\u00e9o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ch\u00ea kh\u00e9o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/17/hlv-can-tho-che-kheo-cau-thu-hagl-nam-san-qua-nhieu.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh ch\u00ea kh\u00e9o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng 19 V-League 2018 di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/7, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 sau c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n To\u00e0n, Osmar Moreira v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Anh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt h\u01a1n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh. Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch cho hay: \"T\u00f4i kh\u00e1 l\u1ea5y l\u00e0m ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng d\u1ed3n l\u00ean nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i s\u1eadp b\u1eaby \u1edf hai b\u00e0n thua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 v\u00e0i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i l\u1eafp gh\u00e9p. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u00f4m nay c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9n \u0111au\u00a0thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p may khi Patiyo v\u00e0 T\u0103ng Tu\u1ea5n b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u1edf n\u1eeda cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai, HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cM\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c pha n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HAGL. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc khi thua, b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean nh\u1eb1m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 thua b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 hai trong hi\u1ec7p 2\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 khi V-League 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. \"Chi\u1ec1u nay S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u00e3 thua Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a BVN. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1\u00a0s\u1ebd tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\", HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-cua-hagl-truoc-can-tho-168-191193.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-cua-hagl-truoc-can-tho.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-cua-hagl-truoc-can-tho-168-191193.html\">HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1?</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 19 V-League tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4227","checkdouble":"191195"},{"date":"19:53 14/07","title":"N\u00d3NG: Eden Hazard s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/nongs-hazard-sap-co-ben-do-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo chia s\u1ebb t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea, Brian Laudrup th\u00ec ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chia tay CLB Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eden chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n sang Real Madrid</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u00d3NG Eden Hazard s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u00d3NG Eden Hazard s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/NONG-Eden-Hazard-sap-co-ben-do-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chuy\u1ec3n sang Real Madrid</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Hazard v\u1edbi CLB Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o hai n\u0103m n\u1eefa. Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y hai b\u00ean v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi nhau \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn m\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Hazard \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n chia tay The Blues v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 sau m\u1ed9t ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, Brian Laudrup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, danh th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch cho r\u1eb1ng Eden Hazard s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Eden Hazard v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\u00a0Eden \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid\u00a0v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t cho c\u1ea3 anh \u1ea5y l\u1eabn Real.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eden l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi h\u01a1n anh \u1ea5y trong c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u1ed9t ch\u1ecdi m\u1ed9t, v\u00ec Hazard c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y c\u1ea3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, anh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t c\u00e1 t\u00ednh v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eden Hazard n\u0103m nay 27 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 anh c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng vinh quang trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Real \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Ronaldo, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110T B\u1ec9 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Bernabeu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng Real \u0111\u00e3 ra gi\u00e1 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh cho Eden Hazard. V\u00e0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec3n khai sau khi World Cup 2018 k\u1ebft th\u00fac.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/_102527296_jorginho_getty2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span><br>\r\nChelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge t\u1eeb Napoli v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-chot-gia-ban-eden-hazard-cho-real-172-191169.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/NONG-Eden-Hazard-sap-co-ben-do-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-chot-gia-ban-eden-hazard-cho-real-172-191169.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real</span><br>\r\nChelsea b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mirror \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/giai-quyet-xong-conte-chelsea-chuan-bi-don-lien-3-tan-binh-172-191166.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/che.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/giai-quyet-xong-conte-chelsea-chuan-bi-don-lien-3-tan-binh-172-191166.html\">Gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft xong Conte, Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n li\u1ec1n 3 t\u00e2n binh</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m t\u00e2n HLV Sarri, v\u00e0 Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n 3 t\u00e2n binh trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4226","checkdouble":"191182"},{"date":"19:41 14/07","title":"Boreham Wood 0-8 Arsenal: Tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/boreham-wood-vs-arsenal-giao-huu-clb-hom-nay.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a HLV Emery tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \"nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u\" t\u1edbi t\u1eeb h\u1ea1ng b\u00e1n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. Trong \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t hattrick.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Do l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u00e8 2018, l\u1ea1i trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m di\u1ec5n ra World Cup 2018 n\u00ean t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Arsenal ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 quy t\u1ee5 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf Nga (do \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i) th\u00ec v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i th\u00eam, ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. D\u1eabu v\u1eady v\u1edbi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi Unai Emery, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf Arsene Wenger v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i, \"Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7\" v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i t\u1ec7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 sao tr\u1ebb.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/14/Boreham-Wood-vs-Arsenal_mp4_Output_1.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong khung g\u1ed7 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea5y n\u0103m qua, Petr Cech. \u1ede h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Bellerin, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i s\u1ed1 1 CLB trong khi tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Aubameyang vs Lacazette. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi Sokratis Papastathopoulos, trung v\u1ec7 30 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n t\u1eeb Dortmund v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 19 tri\u1ec7u Euro. S\u1ed1 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1ebb m\u00e0 trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean t\u1eebng ra s\u00e2n \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 \u1edf c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League nh\u01b0 Maitland-Niles, Willock hay Nelson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Qu\u00e2n xanh\" \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong h\u00e8 2018 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng: Boreham  Wood, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf h\u1ea1ng b\u00e1n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i Anh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t  \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 thua xa v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, Arsenal d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfm th\u1ebf \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i  khai cu\u1ed9c d\u00f9 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \"ch\u1eafp v\u00e1\". V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t h\u01a1n 6 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau  c\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng trong ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i si\u00eau h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0m ch\u00e1y g\u00f3c l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Aubameyang, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o  \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n (ghi 10 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i  Premier League 2017/18).\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Boreham Wood vs Arsenal giao h\u1eefu CLB 21h00 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Boreham Wood vs Arsenal giao h\u1eefu CLB 21h00 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Truc-tiep-Boreham-Wood-vs-Arsenal-giao-huu-CLB-21h00-hom-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Aubameyang l\u1eadp hattrick ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 17 ph\u00fat</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean 2-0. Maitland-Niles, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 ng\u01b0\u1eddi  Anh \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 c\u1ee7a Boreham Wood r\u1ed3i  t\u1ea1t thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb s\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean ngang cho Aubameyang lao v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh  tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. C\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 16, c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia t\u0103ng l\u00ean 3 b\u00e0n. Reiss Nelson, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7  sinh n\u0103m 1999 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Wenger s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng  m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m, Aubameyang nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng  ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa hattrick.</p>\r\n<p>Ph\u00fat 24, ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba Arsenal tr\u1edf n\u00ean  h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n sau m\u1ed9t pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd v\u00e0o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Cech, m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i  b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London m\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb rung l\u00ean. Ph\u00fat 33, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi CH Czech  ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i ra tay c\u1ee9u nguy cho \"Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7\". Tuy nhi\u00ean, ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi  c\u1ee7a Boreham Wood \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i rung l\u00ean l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 4 sau \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c h\u00e3m b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng ng\u1ef1c r\u1ed3i  vu\u1ed1t m\u00e1 ngo\u00e0i k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Nelson t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o do Lacazette th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n.</p>\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 40, Lacazette \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ean l\u00ean b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed v\u1edbi pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ecm  ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n xu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Aubameyang. 0-5 l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1. Sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao, HLV Emery quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Trong danh s\u00e1ch 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i 1 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0 Mustafi,  Mkhitaryan, Ramsey, Chambers, Kolasinac. Ph\u00fat 53, Kolasinac c\u0103ng ngang kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb  Nketiah (sinh n\u0103m 1999) b\u0103ng v\u00e0o d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tung n\u00f3c l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery da co man khoi dau tung bung o Arsenal\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u1edf Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/4E3E423900000578-0-image-a-71_1531584586775.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u1edf Arsenal</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n trong tay c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Boreham Woold c\u1ee9  kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3. Ph\u00fat 66, Ramsey \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng  b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd do l\u1ed7i vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u00e0i ph\u00fat sau, b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 7 \u0111\u00e3  xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. T\u1eeb kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch h\u01a1n 25m, Reine-Adelaide (ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p sinh  n\u0103m 1998) tung ra c\u00fa n\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e1c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 79, Kolasinac chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng s\u1ec7t v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 Mkhitaryan, c\u1ef1u  ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Man Utd, \u0111\u00e3 b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng t\u1ec9a v\u1ec1 g\u00f3c xa \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1  b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 8 cho Arsenal \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, \"Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7\" th\u00e0nh London kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i m\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp  t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 sao, tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e1 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng, \u0111em l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng cho c\u00e1c C\u0110V\u00a0Arsenal. Sau \u0111\u00e2y, Arsenal s\u1ebd bay sang Singapore thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 g\u1eb7p Atletico Madrid vs PSG trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 ICC\u00a02018.\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a Arsenal: </strong>Cech, Bellerin, Sokratis, Mavropanos, Osei-Tutu, Maitland-Niles, Willock, Smith Rowe, Nelson, Aubameyang, Lacazette<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4225","checkdouble":"191183"},{"date":"20:49 14/07","title":"Ch\u00e1n M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/chan-mu-pogba-co-dong-thai-san-sang-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi BL\u0110 Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a anh kh\u1ecfi M.U trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Pogba s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" title=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/chan-mu-pogba-co-dong-thai-san-sang-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Paul Pogba \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U \u0111\u1ec3&nbsp;\u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u00e2n Barca, Mundo Deportivo \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n &ldquo;si\u00eau c\u00f2&rdquo; Mino Raiola &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn bay t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng t\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap Pogba hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gia nh\u1eadp Man United v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, Pogba t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m 2015, Barca t\u1eebng kh\u00e1t khao s\u1edf h\u1eefu Pogba nh\u01b0ng l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Juve. Sau \u0111\u00f3, anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi M.U ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean su\u1ed1t hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u1ea1i Old Trafford, Pogba \u0111ang t\u00ednh t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 La Liga, Barcelona, n\u01a1i m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a anh nh\u01b0 Griezmann hay Umtiti \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho Barca, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chia tay c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 Paulinho.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Pogba, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Barca c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd hai ng\u00f4i sao mang qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 PSG Adrien Rabiot v\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Sevilla, Steven Nzonzi cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-137-mu-co-nguy-co-lon-de-mat-pogba-184-191118.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/30/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-137-mu-co-nguy-co-lon-de-mat-pogba.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-137-mu-co-nguy-co-lon-de-mat-pogba-184-191118.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 13/7: M.U c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Pogba</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 13/7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pogba-khong-dam-coi-thuong-croatia-421-191079.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/pogba-khong-dam-coi-thuong-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pogba-khong-dam-coi-thuong-croatia-421-191079.html\">Pogba n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Croatia?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Croatia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-phat-bieu-soc-ve-mbappe-469-191061.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/pogba-phat-bieu-soc-ve-mbappe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-phat-bieu-soc-ve-mbappe-469-191061.html\">Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i Mbappe v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh anh c\u00f2n k\u00e9m h\u01a1n Mbappe \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 19.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;&#10;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#111000\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4224","checkdouble":"191187"},{"date":"21:36 14/07","title":"Th\u00eam b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y M.U s\u1eafp c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 M.U.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn M.U</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Inter Milan c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 cho Croatia, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Perisic \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a CLB M.U.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, HLV Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Inter \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng th\u00eam chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Perisic s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang tr\u00e1i hay ph\u1ea3i. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 Mourinho s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Perisic \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Perisic \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/dai-dien-cua-perisic-co-mat-tai-manchester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Perisic \u0111ang th\u1ecfa lu\u1eadn v\u1edbi BL\u0110 M.U</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Perisic t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh cho anh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ng\u1ee3i khen: \u201cPerisic l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. B\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 nhanh v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. Nh\u01b0ng Perisic c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t kh\u1ecfe n\u1eefa. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Perisic gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong pha tranh ch\u1ea5p tay \u0111\u00f4i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Mandzukic ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u1ecfe. Perisic th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdn \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ivan Perisic tuy nhi\u00ean ph\u00eda M.U \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi l\u00ean t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 ph\u00eda Inter y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Tuy nhi\u00ean khi m\u00e0 Perisic \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao t\u1ea1i World Cup m\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u2018chi kh\u1ee7ng\u2019 \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mirror (Anh) \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Perisic \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn M.U \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Perisic t\u1edbi M.U s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac ngay trong th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-san-sang-lam-dieu-la-lung-neu-croatia-vo-dich-421-191168.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/rakitic-san-sang-lam-dieu-la-lung-neu-croatia-vo-dich.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rakitic-san-sang-lam-dieu-la-lung-neu-croatia-vo-dich-421-191168.html\">Rakitic s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1ea1 l\u00f9ng n\u1ebfu Croatia v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Zlatko Dalic l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Rakitic s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111i x\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-chuyen-toi-ngoai-hang-anh-421-191158.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/hlv-croatia-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-chuyen-toi-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-chuyen-toi-ngoai-hang-anh-421-191158.html\">HLV Croatia n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?</span><br>\r\nHLV Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-diem-mat-3-cap-doi-dau-dang-cho-doi-421-191119.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-diem-mat-3-cap-doi-dau-dang-cho-doi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-diem-mat-3-cap-doi-dau-dang-cho-doi-421-191119.html\">Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1eb7t 3 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang ta \u00edt gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 n\u1eefa. V\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2u s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup-469-191113.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/modric-toi-san-sang-doi-3-cup-c1-de-vo-dich-world-cup-469-191113.html\">Modric: T\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i 4 c\u00fap C1 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Modric kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi anh. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u Champions...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:\" arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:#111000\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4223","checkdouble":"191192"}]}